{"id":"b9028a35-bf60-4220-a088-088b1082cadd","title":"1540/07: To Lionardo di Buonarroti","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"205a07b1-9127-4d09-bf92-d645002ea72e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [July ..., 1540]","standoffProperties":[{"id":"a7468c54-c37d-43f8-9653-a6cdd06fdc27","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fe57bd19-1dc4-4abb-8686-f6fc0969813e","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ada1e08b-097c-4f17-8170-2276f9599574","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":25,"value":"add0cc60-32c8-4d2a-abea-52b5803e0fda","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"7005dce0-4d3b-4c8d-b8a1-28949bd58587","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo Buonarroti,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"6008a31d-e332-4e0e-a8c8-0625e1263f29","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":21,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"30f9d762-7e6b-4787-acf0-68d51f7b090b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":21,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"bcd73c27-575a-4f7a-89d4-42e6d23e2496","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"ebeadc00-100e-44a6-a9e3-e60ac544e735","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"89573d73-5865-43a7-be6a-5c23e733296f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"8be1b7d0-3ad0-4a4a-88c1-71d761b2818a","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"06839d15-a518-4ffb-85e1-e18182a5d9a5","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I have received thy letter and with it the three shirts. I am very much surprised that ye should have sent them to me, for they are so coarse that there is not a farm labourer here who would not be ashamed to wear them. Even if they had been made of thinner material I wish ye had not sent them:\u00A0when I want shirts I will send the money to buy them. With regard to the farm at Pazzolatica, within\u00A0fifteen or twenty days I will have seven hundred\u00A0ducats paid to Bonifazio Fazi for the purchase thereof; but first it will be necessary to see what\u00A0arrangement Michele has made, so that thy sister, if ever she has occasion to do so, may be able to withdraw the amount of her dowry which is invested in\u00A0the farm. However, thou hadst better discuss it with Gismondo and then write to me; for unless I feel\u00A0assured that there is good security for the seven\u00A0hundred ducats I shall not send the money. I have nothing further to add. Exhort Mona Margerita to\u00A0be of good cheer, and see that thou treat her well\u00A0both in word and deed: behave in all things as an upright man should, otherwise I will make it clear to\u00A0thee that thou shalt enjoy no share of anything that\u00A0is mine.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"1461870d-2368-4812-9bc1-458a45083648","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"19ba253c-9f98-48b8-a49f-eccd03458eb7","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fca4100f-ec02-4828-9e61-bf34816add9d","type":"codex/meta-relation-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"bd4fc623-b318-4587-9e4c-afd86c3844e0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b08c4171-62f1-41d9-b377-8edeaed98ce5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":12,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"fe376897-da46-4ceb-9c48-d5f785a7c691","type":"codex/entity-reference",